text: Prosipho glacialis is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Buccinidae, the true whelks. ==References== * Engl, W. (2012). Shells of Antarctica. Hackenheim: Conchbooks. 402 pp. ==External links== * Category:Buccinidae Category:Gastropods described in 1912
title: Prosipho glacialis
